column5: Hey all, for those of you who weren't here last year we held an online auction immediatley following the Fishing for Tyler G2G.  This year will be no different.  The auction will begin Saturday night and end on Friday night.  I'm not going to tell you what items will be put on the auction block so be sure to check it out.  I will tell you this year we have some really great items up for grabs thanks to some great people in this amazing community.  Maureen
Keep up the great work Maureen and I'll be watching for it.  Mike
